[ Milestone
	Ghost mode.
	Party experience share.
	Protocol 8.21 support.
	More lua functions.
	More configurable things.
	Cleanups & code optimizations.
]

[ Deprecated
	NPC XML attribute autowalk.
		If autowalk used to be 1, walkinterval should be set to 1500.
		If autowalk used to be 0, walkinterval should be set to 0.

		Linux command (make sure you are in data/npc/):
			sed -i 's/autowalk="1"/walkinterval="1500"/g' *.xml && sed -i 's/autowalk="0"/walkinterval="0"/g' *.xml
]

